parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive tongue weight can cause loss of control, trailer sway, and accidents, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
Failure of the 5th wheel trailer hitch can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle and trailer, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
The failure of the rear axle lugs can cause the wheel to shear off, leading to a loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The wheel suddenly comes loose or falls off while driving
the vehicle pulls to one side
unusual vibrations or noises from the rear axle
